data.description: Super Spacious and ready for your personal touch!! 4 bedroom 2.5 bath two-story home with  formal living room, decorative pillars throughout , gas fireplace, formal dining room, custom kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, breakfast bar, deep farm sink, stainless steel appliances (kitchen refrigerator will not remain with the home after sale) ,and two pantries in the kitchen. The primary bedroom has lighted tray ceilings, a bathroom with a jetted tub as well as a stand- up shower, and a walk-in closet. There is a second floor family room could double as your home office. Outside you have a two car garage, double-wide driveway, covered front porch, and fenced backyard with a patio area great for entertaining. Schedule you personal showing today!
